onyxplatform.test

Class SingleCljTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • onyxplatform.test.JobBuilder
      • onyxplatform.test.SingleCljTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnyxNames

    public class SingleCljTest
extends JobBuilder
implements OnyxNames
    SingleCljTest tests a Job running with a single clojure function. All basic behavior is set up using the JobBuilder base class, while the clojure method to be used is bound to the namespace within the constructor. Note that any clojure function used in an onyx job task must be loaded in the way demonstrated in this class.
